  "market_context": "On 3 May 2024, CL1! was trading within a defined daily range bounded by a clear range high and range low. London session failed to take out either side of the range, producing no significant directional move and leaving both sides of the range intact entering the New York session.",
  "key_observation": "At the 08:30–09:30 NY kill zone, price swept both the range low and the range high in sequence, creating a series of up-close candles on the 5-minute chart that constituted a Change in the State of Delivery (CHoCH), signaling a bearish reversal opportunity.",
  "analysis_steps": [
    "Step 1: Identified the daily range by marking the Range High and Range Low on the 15-minute chart for 3 May 2024.",
    "Step 2: Observed that London session failed to take out either side of the range, confirming no directional London move and classifying the profile as NY Manipulation.",
    "Step 3: Noted a failure swing forming within the range during London, reinforcing that neither side had been swept.",
    "Step 4: Watched the 08:30 and 09:30 NY time levels; at those times price swept the range low and then also swept the range high.",
    "Step 5: Dropped to the 5-minute chart and identified a series of up-close candles forming on the new high, marking this as the Change in the State of Delivery (CHoCH) / bearish signal.",
    "Step 6: Planned a short entry at the CHoCH level with a stop-loss placed above the swept high.",
    "Step 7: Set the take-profit target at the opposite side of the range (range low), calculated to be 1.75R.",
    "Step 8: Confirmed entry was tagged and price delivered to the target at the other side of the range."
  ],
  "outcome": "Short entry triggered after the NY sweep and CHoCH on the 5-minute chart; price moved to the opposite side of the range, hitting the 1.75R target successfully.",
  "lessons": "When London consolidates without taking either side of the daily range, the NY Manipulation profile is likely: New York will sweep one or both sides to create a CHoCH before delivering to the true target. Enter on the 5M CHoCH with stop above the manipulation high and target the opposite range boundary.",
